The objective of the game is simple, try to hit the moving player on the right half of the board.
The left player is controlled using w,a,s,d and simply fire a bullet by left clicking the computer mouse.
The game has a UI that allows the players to navigate the game and change features like the settings.

The Difficulty can be changed in multiple ways:
-The bulletAmount Variable; #Number of bullets that can be on the screen at one time (Larger value is easier, Smaller value is harder)
-The bulletSpeed Variable; #The speed at which the bullets travel (Larger value is easier, Smaller value is harder)
-The moveCounterSpeed Variable; #The amount of time it takes for the AI to change its direction (Larger value is harder, Smaller value is easier)
-The movementSpeed Variable; #The speed at which the AI will move (Larger value is harder, Smaller value is easier)